    prompt: 'Download and set up a meditation timer app with interval bells to structure your device-free reflection periods',
    category: 'planning',
    helpText: 'Structured meditation and reflection time helps fill the mental space previously occupied by digital stimulation and builds your capacity for sustained focus without devices. Choose a simple meditation timer app like Insight Timer or Enso that offers interval bells and gentle background sounds, then practice using it for 10-15 minute sessions during your first week of detox. This tool bridges the gap between digital dependency and complete disconnection while developing mindfulness skills that support your overall digital wellness goals.'
