  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-45',
    prompt: 'Configure your router and home WiFi to automatically disable internet access during designated detox hours',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Network-level controls create the strongest barriers to digital access and eliminate the possibility of bypassing individual device restrictions during your committed offline time. Access your router\'s admin panel and set up scheduled WiFi shutdowns or internet restrictions during your planned detox hours, such as evening family time or weekend mornings. This comprehensive approach ensures that all household devices lose connectivity simultaneously, preventing you from switching between phones, tablets, or computers when one is blocked. Having to physically restart your router creates significant friction that supports your commitment to digital boundaries.'
  }</parameter>
